](url)
Risks:
- Due to FlatHash not being thread safe, it is guarded with a readwritelock. There is some risk of contention on the lock if many concurrent equality deletes are all read and inserted into the FlatHash at the same time. This is probably not a problem in practice given equality delete loading is IO bound for norma

